m-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">C</span></span><span>Open screen capture</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd Shift S</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">Q</span></span><span>Open quick settings</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd Shift Q</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">N</span></span><span>Show notification center</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd Shift N</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">B</span></span><span>Switch to Browser</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd 2</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">M</span></span><span>Set motion: reduced</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd 2</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">A</span></span><span>Set wallpaper: aurora</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd 7</span></div><div class=\"wm-command-item\" role=\"option\"><span class=\"wm-taskbar-icon wm-round-icon\"><span class=\"wm-icon-glyph\">W</span></span><span>Open widget gallery</span><span class=\"wm-command-shortcut\">Cmd G</span></div></div>\n"
